  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Glucocorticoid treatment for ≥ 3 months with a prednisone dose of ≥ 7.5mg/d or
             equivalent glucocorticoid

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Refusal of informed consent

          -  Prior therapy with metformin during the last 6 month

          -  Preexisting diabetes

          -  Pregnancy or current malignancy

          -  Renal insufficiency with a creatinine clearance lower than 30ml/min
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
